"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-moulin-rouge-windmill-sails-restored-collapse-paris-olympics-montmartre\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  Updated on:  July 6, 2024 / 9:36 AM EDT/ CBS/AP  The famous Moulin Rouge cabaret in Paris got its iconic red windmill back on Friday just in time for theSummer Olympicslater this month.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"score\": 0.999108137229772, \"rank\": 0.0004978641731731757, \"text\": \"CBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS\"}, {\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512972412674381e-36, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999633928, \"rank\": 3.670735924589853e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mill's huge sails inexplicably collapsed after a show in April at the iconic venue, an emblem of the surrounding Montmartre neighborhood.\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When the sails fell, they took with them the first three letters of the Moulin Rouge sign.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's sad, just sad,\\\" Danish tourist Lars Thygesen toldCBS News at the time.\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope they will build it up again, so it will be as it always has been, the old Moulin Rouge,\\\" added his partner Lise.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512972412674381e-36, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lise_de_Baissac\", \"score\": 0.9782327381512211, \"rank\": 0.018228475787990972, \"text\": \"Lise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lise_de_Baissac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lise_de_Baissac\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one was hurt and the mayor of Paris' 18th district said the structure was not in danger.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999633928, \"rank\": 3.670735924589853e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Moulin Rouge scrambled to repair the damage before July 15, when the Olympic torch relay is expected to draw big crowds as it passes through the area.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512972412674381e-36, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, a special ceremony that featured can-can dancing on the plaza outside marked the restoration.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The windmill was first illuminated on Oct. 6, 1889, at the opening of the Moulin Rouge.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512972412674381e-36, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cabaret, marking its 135th anniversary this year, is a major tourist attraction and was celebrated in the 2001 Baz Luhrmann film musical starring Nicole Kidman.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8057212459948172e-34, \"text\": \"Nicole Kidman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cabaret management says its performers represent 18 nationalities and it receives 600,000 spectators a year.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten, or redistributed.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this report.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999813074026355, \"rank\": 1.869009944314446e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q242